title: Episode 100 w/ the Drink Champs family
itunes:title: Episode 100 w/ the Drink Champs family
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys celebrate they're 100th episode by talking about some of their favorite Drink Champs moments. We hear from some of the members of the D.C. family about their favorite memories and about their roles within in the D.C. organization and family. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
